    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693350/extras/b66714a9ec12adbd3a850cc66bedd20c.avif?t=1770888744\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693350/extras_big/b66714a9ec12adbd3a850cc66bedd20c.avif?t=1770888744 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore 8 Unique Worlds:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore 8 wildly different environments throughout the solar system in search of your ex-girlfriend, Kat. Revisit them with better equipment to uncover things you might've missed before!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693350/extras/c40dd9a7f635a3b8dd2e85e6df3da98e.avif?t=1770888744\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693350/extras_big/c40dd9a7f635a3b8dd2e85e6df3da98e.avif?t=1770888744 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Upgrade Weapons &amp; Equipment:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you fulfill your contracts, you'll get paid. Purchase upgrades for your weapons &amp; equipment so you can more easily defeat different types of enemies &amp; conquer the various challenges of the environments on each new world you explore. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693350/extras/1d4779ac9c18656634abf7f0557f2a9e.avif?t=1770888744\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693350/extras_big/1d4779ac9c18656634abf7f0557f2a9e.avif?t=1770888744 width=800 height=730 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story &amp; Characters:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kat has been corrupted by the evil Church of the Black Star. Your overarching goal is to track her down.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693350/extras/9528da8cb17514704ea0e8d5389c0eb2.avif?t=1770888744\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693350/extras_big/9528da8cb17514704ea0e8d5389c0eb2.avif?t=1770888744 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our mission has been to create a game that is funny &amp; wholesome while still harkening back to our favorite game protagonists of the 90s. Bird puns, one-liners, &amp; zany animal characters are a staple of the experience we've created. Each level contains both unique &amp; mainstay enemies to keep you in the rhythm, but on your toes. </p>",
